    "description": "Discipline: Waijia\nSkill: Light Melee against Parry\nType: Normal\nQi: 3\n\nYou deliver an upward strike that sends your opponent bouncing into the air with each blow you land. On a Success you send your foe up into the air 5 feet per Rank of Waijia, doing normal Damage. The person lands the next round, taking normal falling Damage, unless you choose to strike again (sending them back up into the air). Cathartic: When done in this manner, you may use Stick of the Rebounding Dog as a Move action, allowing you to Attack or perform Skills while you bounce your target in the air each round.",
